Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time spent on cases involving 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER and the end of the case

Name: Average resolution time for cases with 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER and the end of the case

Name: Time difference between 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' for cases where both occur
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' in cases where rejection is overturned
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total resolution time of cases with 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' compared to cases without it
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER does not occur

Name: Minimun time from 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Request Payment' in cases where payment is still requested
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Time from 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' in cases of re-submission after rejection
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average waiting time to 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' from the start of the case
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Minimun resolution time of cases with 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' compared to those with 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER and the end of the case

Name: Total time from 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Payment Handled' in cases where payment is eventually made
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Payment Handled'
